The **~FullTextSearch** [[Help:WikiPlugin|plugin]] performs searches on ~InterWiki sites listed in InterWikiMap.

== Usage ==
{{{
<<InterWikiSearch arguments>>
}}}

== Arguments ==

{| class="bordered"
|-
! Argument
! Description
! Default value
|-
| **s**
| The search term
| //none//
|-
| **formsize**
|
| 30
|}

== Example ==

{{{
<<InterWikiSearch>>
}}}

<<InterWikiSearch>>

